"Krähling H., Saffert R., Spindler E.-J.","PVC-plastisols - problem solvers in the automotive industry [PVC-Plastisole - Problemloeser im Automobilbau]",1999,"KGK-Kautschuk und Gummi Kunststoffe","52","7",,"477","481",,,,"http://www.scopus.com/inward/record.url?eid=2-s2.0-0032669483&partnerID=40&md5=30fc0f3e40c6f802ad194da54b7ea8a4","Vinnolit Kunststoff GmbH, Burghausen, Germany; Vinnolit Kunststoff GmbH, Johannes-Hess-Straße 24, D-84489 Burghausen, Germany","Krähling, H., Vinnolit Kunststoff GmbH, Burghausen, Germany; Saffert, R., Vinnolit Kunststoff GmbH, Burghausen, Germany; Spindler, E.-J., Vinnolit Kunststoff GmbH, Burghausen, Germany, Vinnolit Kunststoff GmbH, Johannes-Hess-Straße 24, D-84489 Burghausen, Germany","Ecobalance calculations confirm the competitiveness of PVC plastisols for automotive underbody coatings when ecological criteria are considered as e.g. energy consumption or global warming potential. The consideration of risk potentials during production, processing, use and waste management reveal that PVC underbody systems and their alternatives have not shown special problems up to now. The residual components of automotive underbody coatings are safely controlled with regard to metal recycling and conversion of the light shredder residues.",,"Automobile materials; Automotive industry; Coatings; Ecology; Environmental protection; Polyvinyl chlorides; Recycling; Waste disposal; Automotive underbody coatings; Light shredder residues; Plastisols",,,,,,"Symietz, D., Unterbodenschutz und Abdichtungen beim Auto (1994) Kunststoffe, 84, p. 1611; (1996) Stiftung Arbeit und Umwelt, Ökologische Effizienz Gemeinsam Gestalten; Schönemann, H., Krähling, H., Von Flotow, P., Ökobilanzen im Werkstoffentscheidungsprozeß (1996) VDI Berichte, 1307, p. 331; (1997) Systempartnerschaft, Kunden-Lieferanten-Kooperationen für Zukunftsfähige Produkte, Ergebnisse Eines Pilotprojektes, Ökologische Wettbewerbsfähigkeit Calciumcarbonatgefüllter PVC- und Styrol-Methacrylat-Unter